name: Tempo, Intensive Zone 6 #2
description:
It's always easier to produce high power when fresh. Today's session requires you to build up some fatigue through a 30-minute tempo effort before completing 5 x 45-second high power efforts. Break up the opening Tempo effort by alternating between standing and seated pedalling.
